## DESTROY
```powershell
# Delete ingresses FIRST - lets ALB controller clean up AWS resources
kubectl delete ingress --all -n registration-app
Start-Sleep -Seconds 90

cd terraform
terraform destroy -auto-approve
```

If destroy fails on subnets: manually delete security groups named
k8s-traffic-* and k8s-registra-* in AWS Console, then retry.

